{"name": "odoo14-addon-mail-improved-tracking-value", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-mail-improved-tracking-value", "version": "14.0.1.0.1", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/social", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Improves tracking changed values for certain type of fields.Adds a user-friendly view to consult them.", "upload_time": 1698476743}, "documentation": ["```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.svg\n:alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n:target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n```\n\n# Tracking value change improved\n\nThis module extends the mail_tracking_value functionality that records\nvalue changes on predefined fields.\nIt adds support for many2many and one2many fields, which are not handled\nwell by default.\nIt also implements a new view (little bit more user friendly than the\nexisting one) to watch for changes\n\n## Installation\n\nTo install this module, you need to:\n\n1. Just install the module\n\n## Configuration\n\nTo configure this module, you need to:\n\n\\# No configuration is necessary\n\n## Usage\n\nTo access the new view displaying value changes :\n\n> Settings -> Technical -> Improved tracking values\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\n> - Improve rendering of values depending of type using qweb widgets\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/mail_improved_tracking_value/issues). In case of trouble, please\ncheck there if your issue has already been reported. If you spotted it first,\nhelp us smash it by providing detailed and welcomed feedback.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Images\n\n- Odoo Community Association: [Icon](https://github.com/OCA/maintainer-tools/blob/master/template/module/static/description/icon.svg).\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Thierry Ducrest \\<<mailto:thierry.ducrest@camptocamp.com>>\n\n### Maintainer\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nTo contribute to this module, please visit <https://odoo-community.org>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.models", "documentation": ["Copyright 2017 Camptocamp SA", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.models.mail_tracking_value", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.models..mail_tracking_value", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 Camptocamp SA", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.models", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value..models", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.tests.test_improved_tracking_value", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.tests..test_improved_tracking_value", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.__manifest__", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 Camptocamp SA", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_improved_tracking_value.models.mail_tracking_